from tony alicea subject southern baptist convention freemasonry with the southern baptist convention convene thi june to consider the charge that freemasonry be incompatible with christianity i think the follow quote by mr jame holly the anti-masonic flag carrier would amuse you all the follow passage be exact quote from the southern baptist convention and freemasonry by jame l holly president of mission and ministry to man inc n st beaumont tx the inside cover of the book state mission ministry to man inc hereby grant permission for the reproduction of part or all of thi booklet with two provision one the material be not change and two the source be identify i have follow these provision freemasonry be one of the ally of the devil page iv the issue here be not moderate or conservative the issue be god and the devil page vus it be worthwhile to remember that the formulator of public school education in america be freemason page jesu christ never command toleration a a motive for hi disciple and toleration be the antithesi of the christian message page the central dynamic of the freemason drive for world unity through fraternity liberty and equality be toleration thi be see in the write of the writer of freemasonry page he jesu christ establish the most sectarian of all possible faith page for narrownes and sectarianism there be no equal to the lord jesu christ page what seem so right in the interest of toleration and it cousins-liberty equality and fraternity-i actually one of the subtlest ly of the of ly page the southern baptist convention ha many church which be found in the lodge and which have corner stone dedicate by the lodge each of these church should hold public ceremoney of repentance and of pray the blood and the name of the lord jesu christ over the church and renounce the oath take at the dedication of the church build page tony 